snippet.textDisplay:
It should be Gilli Gilli "Banni" ae ni Sammiye, not "Baani". Banni is a raised ground, usually a path. Here it goes thus: Gilli gilli Banni ae ni Sammiye, Pair sambhalke uttariye ni Sammiye (O Sammi, the path is wet, land carefully).

Otherwise, beautifully song, listen to it everyday.
